  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><strong>Monday 19th September 2016, Godalming, Surrey-</strong> As Summer 2016 comes to a close at Inghams we are looking forward to another successful ski season as well as turning our thoughts to Summer 2017.</p>
<p><br />Inghams <a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays">Lakes and Mountains</a> Summer 2017 programme features some of the finest scenic holidays, walking and tours in Europe with a choice of 7 countries and flights from 23 regional airports. Highlights of the summer 2017 programme include;</p>
<p><br />• <a data-udi="umb://document/f9c8f69f2d2844faa33d9d63d5bcd0f2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f9c8f69f2d2844faa33d9d63d5bcd0f2}" title="Treasures of Tuscany">A new Treasures of Tuscany tour</a><br />• New resort combination ‘Lakes and Peaks’ combining- a two centred holiday in either <a data-udi="umb://document/0fa258c1078147e4be5f442c15be3088" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fa258c1078147e4be5f442c15be3088}" title="St. Wolfgang">St. Wolfgang</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/d2df326fd2d544f2b9d4699c3cf10233" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d2df326fd2d544f2b9d4699c3cf10233}" title="Fuschl am See">Fuschl</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/95ff1fe2e71242759843cc1f6b11ccdc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/95ff1fe2e71242759843cc1f6b11ccdc}" title="St. Gilgen">St. Gilgen</a> followed by <a data-udi="umb://document/04e03f5c842c48279d8406095eb78480" href="/{localLink:umb://document/04e03f5c842c48279d8406095eb78480}" title="Berchtesgaden">Berchtesgaden</a> in the Bavarian Alps. <br />• Take your bike to<a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France"> France</a><br />Here’s a roundup of our Top 5 holiday suggestions for Summer 2017 from some of the most loved properties and destinations across the Lakes and Mountains programme.</p>
<p><br /><strong>1. <a data-udi="umb://document/7c2039e31003455f9c5af8c11e6f0e11" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7c2039e31003455f9c5af8c11e6f0e11}" title="Gardone Riviera">Gardone</a>,<a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda"> Lake Garda</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a> –</strong> The 4 diamond Chalet Hotel Galeazzi is a well-loved destination for holiday goers. Only 7 minutes’ walk from the resort centre and 5 minutes from the lakeside promenade this is an unparalleled holiday choice. Lake Garda is a beautiful summer spot with its glistening lake, Italian culture and mouth-watering cuisine. Inghams is offering 7 nights, chalet catering at the <a data-udi="umb://document/abd522701a0549f380ea3e9235c3c817" href="/{localLink:umb://document/abd522701a0549f380ea3e9235c3c817}" title="Chalet Hotel Galeazzi">4 diamond Chalet Hotel Galeazzi</a>, Lake Garda, Italy from £613pp departing May 2017. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Verona and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays">www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays</a> or call 01483 791 116.</p>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/1339/chalet-hotel-galeazzi-gardone-riviera-lake-garda-italy-exterior.jpg" alt="Chalet Hotel Galeazzi" width="486" height="300" rel="486,300" /></p>
<p><br /><strong>2. Reichenau, <a data-udi="umb://document/352137bbbdf44ec4ac7857b5a613deb4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/352137bbbdf44ec4ac7857b5a613deb4}" title="Lake Constance">Lake Constance</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/baf439b4f3004bcdbcf23a91adb08ac5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/baf439b4f3004bcdbcf23a91adb08ac5}" title="Germany">Germany</a> -</strong> a country of history, beauty and diversity, Germany is a lesser known spot for a fantastic holiday especially one on the shores of Lake Constance. Inghams is offering 7 nights half board at the <a data-udi="umb://document/dafc5ea8ecfb44229ab92dd7dd27600a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dafc5ea8ecfb44229ab92dd7dd27600a}" title="Ganter Hotel Mohren (Reichenau)">3.5* Ganter Hotel Mohren</a>, Reinchenau, Lake Constance, germany from £825pp departing may 2017. Price includes return flights from London City and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays%20or%20call%2001483%20791%20116">www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays or call 01483 791 116</a>.</p>
<p><br /><strong>3. Treasures of Tuscany-</strong> <strong>NEW</strong> to the Inghams programme for summer 2017 this tour encapsulated all of the best part of Tuscany including visits to Florence, Siena and San Gimigano blending an intriguing mix of culture, history and picturesque countryside. Inghams is offering 7 nights, Treasures of Tuscany from £1,229 departing September 2017. Price includes services of an Explorer Guide, full day in Florence with a guided tour of the Uffizi gallery, visits to Siena and San Gimignano, a day discovering Chianti, a walking tour of Lucca, time in Montecatini, 7 nights half board accommodation at the Grand Hotel Francia and Quirinale or the Grand Hotel Bellavista Palace in Montecatini, return flights from Lond on Gatwick and transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays">www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays</a> or call 01483 791 116.</p>
<p><br /><strong>4. Lech, Austria-</strong> with stunning walks around the Arlberg area <a data-udi="umb://document/f5a2404579b84c448ac2a43bfaacfdd0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f5a2404579b84c448ac2a43bfaacfdd0}" title="Lech">Lech</a> is the perfect place for avid walkers. Inghams guests receive a free resort card as part of the stay which allows free use of resort cable cars and lifts, free use of the local hiker buses, free use of the open-air swimming pool in Lech, Free entrance to the leisure centre, museum, tennis courts and mini golf, free supervised daily kids club and activity programme, free band, concert and folk lore Inghams is offering 7 nights, chalet catering at the <a data-udi="umb://document/5ae66c30c09043ccb9c7c8d533642e89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5ae66c30c09043ccb9c7c8d533642e89}" title="Chalet Hotel Elisabeth">4 diamond Chalet Hotel Elisabeth</a> from £624pp departing June 2017. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Innsbruck and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays">www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays</a> or call 01483 791 116.</p>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13059933/chalet-hotel-elisabeth-lech-austria-front-exterior.jpg" alt="Ch Elisabeth" width="486" height="300" rel="486,300" /></p>
<p><br /><strong>5. <a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc}" title="Morzine">Morzine</a>, France-</strong> take your own bike to Morzine next summer and explore the mountains which hosted the Tour de France last July. Inghams is offering 7 nights, half board at the 4* Hotel Les Champs Fleuris, Morzine, France from £774 per person, saving £85pp departing 24th June 2017. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Geneva and resort transfers. NEW- add your bike on with a reservations consultant at the time of booking. For more information or to book visit www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays or call 01483 791 116.</p>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13055981/fields-with-chairlifts-overhead.jpg" alt="Morzine Summer" width="486" height="300" rel="486,300" /></p>
